{"type":"article","id":12689,"title":"一张图，看看哪些国家是不保护人权的。","uid":13737,"topics":[401],"contents":"一共18个国际性人权条约，看看每个国家都批准了几个。<br>\n<br>\n当然，批准了条约不等于真的保护人权。这里面的蓝色国家，批准了人权条约，根本就不执行的，不在少数。<br>\n但是，最起码，连签都不肯签的，人权状况必定一塌糊涂。橙色国家就是。<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://anonymousfiles.io/f/OHCHR_Map_AllTreaties.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://anonymousfiles.io/f/OHCHR_Map_AllTreaties.jpg\" alt=\"https://anonymousfiles.io/f/OHCHR_Map_AllTreaties.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-01-22","agreeCount":0,"discussionCount":0}